title: Ministry of Sound UK - EDM Euphoria 3CD (2014) (VBR) (AciDToX8)
description:
Ministry of Sound UK - EDM Euphoria 3CD (2014) 

              Progressive, House, Electro | Ministry of Sound UK

                 VBR | MP3 | unmixed | 2014 | 03:58:41 | 382 Mb


The 2014 edition of 'EDM Euphoria', a compilation of some of the biggest and most anticipated unreleased EDM tracks! Euphoria derived from the over whelming demand of students wanting large scale electronic dance productions. Leveraging the assistance of Student Government Associations, Program Councils, and Greek Life we are able to produce a production that is safe, top-notch and affordable to students around the country. To this day, sound is what epitomises Ministry of Sound and all we stand for. As we spread the dance music gospel around the world you can experience the essence of what we do but there's nothing quite like standing in the middle of the club's main room (The Box).
